## Tyneo Website

The website for Tyneo Consulting. You can see the generated files at tyneo/tyneo-consulting.com repository.

## Getting started
To generate the Tyneo's website, please install nodejs and hexojs first.

1. Download and install NodeJs from https://nodejs.org
2. Install HexoJs from npm :
``` bash
npm install hexo-cli -g
```
3. Clone repository and install dependencies:
``` bash
$ git clone git@jirachi.tyneo.net:tyneo/tyneo-website.git
$ cd tyneo-website
$ npm install
```

Generate:

``` bash
$ hexo generate
```

Run server:

``` bash
$ hexo server
```